== Install and build ==

=== Source ===

Releases can be found at http://exodus.xmms.se/~tru/esperanza/ and the latest devel can be found in [http://git.xmms.se XMMS2 git tree].

=== Dependencies ===

* XMMS2
** XMMS2 C++ bindings, which needs boost.
* Qt 4.1 for 0.1 and 4.2 for git version.

=== Build ===

Download tarball run qmake (or qmake-qt4 depending on your system) and then make. That should produce the binary.

